    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏆 WIN TO EARN — 投注游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特点之一 — WIN TO EARN模式。比赛前，双方玩家用游戏货币下注，形成共同奖池。获胜队伍赢得一切 — 失败者空手而归。最大紧张感，绝不妥协。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014740/extras/7d525ebcecbcbb0a99d353e2fe6400a4.avif?t=1748168447\" width=600 height=253 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👥 战队、竞赛、全球锦标赛</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他玩家联合，建立联盟并在战队战争中称霸。大型奖励锦标赛、排行榜和反作弊系统确保公平激烈的战斗。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔥 武器与角色定制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁25种以上武器，使用200+模块进行升级 — 瞄准镜、配件和其他改进。自定义你的战士外观：装备和配件让你在战场上脱颖而出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014740/extras/f46c29358929d34ff2ce0a84cadd6a6f.poster.avif?t=1748168447\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014740/extras/f46c29358929d34ff2ce0a84cadd6a6f.webm?t=1748168447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014740/extras/f46c29358929d34ff2ce0a84cadd6a6f.mp4?t=1748168447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💰 经济与进度</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过每日任务赚取游戏货币。投资最佳装备，加入战队并参加巨额奖金的锦标赛。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌃 推荐系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用个人促销代码邀请朋友，获得代币、装备和知名度奖励。邀请的人越多，奖励越好！</p>",
